text: Blueprint for Robbery is a 1961 American crime movie directed by Jerry Hooper and starring J. Pat O'Reilly, Robert J. Wilke, Robert Gist, Henry Corden, Tom Duggan, Joe Conley, Marion Ross. It was distributed by Paramount Pictures. ==Other websites== * Category:1961 crime movies Category:American crime movies Category:Paramount Pictures movies Category:Movies directed by Jerry Hooper
title: Blueprint for Robbery
